## Example 1: Basic Usage

### Scenario

```
User asks to solve Problem X using approach Y
```

### Application

WHEN problem_type === "X":
READ problem_requirements INTO requirements
ANALYZE requirements FOR complexity

    IF complexity === "low":
        APPLY basic_pattern
    ELSE:
        APPLY advanced_pattern

    VALIDATE solution
    REPORT results

### Expected Outcome

```
Solution successfully applies pattern Y with verification
```

## Example 2: Advanced Usage

### Scenario

```
Complex multi-step problem requiring pattern composition
```

### Application

DECLARE composite_solution: object
SET composite_solution = {}

FOR EACH sub_problem IN complex_problem:
ANALYZE sub_problem FOR applicable_pattern
APPLY pattern TO sub_problem INTO partial_solution
APPEND partial_solution TO composite_solution.parts

INTEGRATE composite_solution.parts INTO final_solution
VALIDATE final_solution AGAINST full_requirements

### Expected Outcome

```
Composed solution addressing all aspects of complex problem
```

